It could also belong to the Multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category as it deals with image processing and segmentation. 

The paper also introduces a new clustering framework, which could be relevant to the Machine Learning (cs.LG) sub-category. 

The proposed method involves capturing texture information, which could be relevant to the Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) sub-category. 

Finally, the paper deals with image segmentation, which could be relevant to the Graphics (cs.GR) sub-category.
